<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Workers With Disabilities Are Making Cents Per Hour &#8212; and It’s Legal</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="751" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-1200x751.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A woman repackages plastic sprayers at a sheltered workshop for adults with disabilities." itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-1200x751.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-200x125.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-400x250.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-800x501.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop.jpg 1336w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="751" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A woman repackages plastic sprayers at a sheltered workshop for adults with disabilities." itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-1200x751.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-200x125.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-400x250.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-800x501.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop.jpg 1336w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/2019_0606-sheltered-workshop-1200x751.jpg" loading="lazy">
<figcaption class="wp-caption-text" itemprop="caption">A woman repackages plastic sprayers at a sheltered workshop for adults with disabilities. Under a 1938 labor law, people with disabilities are paying the economic price while major corporations get rich.</figcaption><figcaption class="wp-caption-credit" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Tammy Ljungblad / Kansas City Star</span></figcaption></figure></div>
